{"abstract": "To qualify for elite status in hotel loyalty programs, some people go on \u201cmattress runs\u201d: checking into a hotel for no other reason than to accumulate points.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/10/business/games-travelers-play-to-snag-hotel-upgrades.html", "snippet": "To qualify for elite status in hotel loyalty programs, some people go on \u201cmattress runs\u201d: checking into a hotel for no other reason than to accumulate points.", "lead_paragraph": "On Andrew Hazelton\u2019s last trip to Phoenix, he checked into a hotel and walked out, then checked into another room a few miles away. Mr. Hazelton, who travels frequently for his job in film distribution consulting, isn\u2019t a finicky traveler. He is one of a growing cadre of business travelers who go to extraordinary lengths to secure elite-level status at their preferred hotel brand.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "8", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/12/10/business/Mattress1/Mattress1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 381, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2013/12/10/business/Mattress1/Mattress1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 381}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/12/10/business/Mattress1/Mattress1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 650, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/12/10/business/Mattress1/Mattress1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1300, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/12/10/business/Mattress1/Mattress1-thumbStandard.jpg", "